270
00:15:04,536 --> 00:15:05,504
Yeah.

271
00:15:05,537 --> 00:15:07,038
Like world-changing.

272
00:15:07,072 --> 00:15:08,739
Do you pay attention
to anything?

273
00:15:08,772 --> 00:15:11,275
