00:16:18,628 --> 00:16:20,462
Watch it, dickhead!

301
00:16:20,496 --> 00:16:22,131
Sorry, sweetie.

302
00:16:22,164 --> 00:16:23,766
<i>Well, they closed
the dorm at 5:00.</i>

