[alarm sounds]

316
00:17:03,930 --> 00:17:05,332
[silenced gunshot]

317
00:17:05,365 --> 00:17:06,700
[knock at door]

318
00:17:06,733 --> 00:17:09,868
Make like Michael Jackson
