00:17:09,902 --> 00:17:11,604
So I need a huge favor.

320
00:17:12,871 --> 00:17:14,539
No.

321
00:17:14,572 --> 00:17:17,275
Thing is, I have to catch
a flight to Calgary.

322
00:17:17,308 --> 00:17:18,775
Charlie.

323
00:17:18,809 --> 00:17:20,410
You don't have
to keep pretending

