Giddyup, partner.

387
00:21:24,070 --> 00:21:25,604
Nice getup.

388
00:21:27,438 --> 00:21:28,873
Janitorial technician.

389
00:21:30,075 --> 00:21:32,442
Make sure our asset's
on her way out.

390
00:21:32,476 --> 00:21:33,544
Yes, sir.

391
00:21:52,159 --> 00:21:53,760
